{"tid":748104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長毛：美國應考慮廢除《香港關係法》","createTime":"2018-07-19T03:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T04:18:19.000Z","uid":5195,"like":217,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"7bad58b2fd69f4aaea7ba1e3e5a9bd6284dca9b5","tid":748104,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"梁國雄昨日聲稱，自稱「民主派」的議員，包括區議員，應當籌錢在美媒如《華爾街日報》賣廣告，要美國政府考慮廢除《香港關係法》，而只有將港人的「憤怒」「訴諸國際」，引起西方政客的「注意」，才有可能改變現狀云云"},{"pid":"c7a144c3e042bd0b8e4fe28323f1c06ab51a0c69","tid":748104,"uid":17641,"like":99,"dislike":8,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"鳩毛喺度執人口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f51ba831e6ffc248c14395ba83ae6bcf1788254","tid":748104,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"daea71a4b1a98a88d49b24e157324068702255f8","tid":748104,"uid":49388,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"長毛：本土派要求美國放棄香港政策法，加速破壞香港！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/672366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/672366</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad109dde4a21837eed93e687684f326c3c0b6fce","tid":748104,"uid":134864,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"G持攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99380f0526a970eda900909372ad28e0264b4154","tid":748104,"uid":13663,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"梁國雄指，行動最實際，呼籲自稱民主派的議員，包括區議員，在短期內籌錢在美媒如《華爾街日報》賣廣告，內容是問美國人「香港是否成為中華人民共和國一部分？若是，《對港關係法》亦可以廢除。」梁國雄又說，林鄭不會理會他們的意見，只有在短期內成功將市民的忿怒「訴諸國際」，引起西方政客的注意，才有可能改變，包括發起實名簽名運動和呼籲他們加入「捐錢賣廣告」的行列。他提醒，政府趁立法會休會取締民族黨，是試圖「偷雞」，呼籲大家要「企出來」，讓林鄭不能得逞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500c61bbf1922ef7947494212469bb76bc085ce9","tid":748104,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"侵B 100"},{"pid":"994e571edd6263257cf1ee09b8751d60fbed5f62","tid":748104,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"長毛咪試吓係民陣集會<br />\n睇吓有幾多人捐？"},{"pid":"089195a630fde0a0b61cb90002e46e87f9aa4128","tid":748104,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"係香港生果登咪一樣<br />\n如果生果肯登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會捐"},{"pid":"16c22ef404d44040050b4398e9e5a4c6cd51701e","tid":748104,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75295e70cc6c51c9c13f41398236207f6fdf148","tid":748104,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ac1cb1a5d8eb37a24702d5529254f6827c142b","tid":748104,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"daea71a4b1a98a88d49b24e157324068702255f8","tid":748104,"uid":49388,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"長毛：本土派要求美國放棄香港政策法，加速破壞香港！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/672366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/672366</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8e8d588bcdaca196fb350334515e3e3af64916","tid":748104,"uid":181655,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"支持一獲熟！寧死不屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/